==Russian==
[[Category:Russian adjectives]]
===Etymology===
From [[совет]] (sovét), "advice," "council."

===Adjective===
'''советский''', советская, советское, советские (sovétskij, sovétskaja, sovétskoje, sovétskije) ''m/f/n/pl''

